data.description: Welcome home. This spacious home offers two rooms, one bathroom. Recently remodeled kitchen, flooring and lighting. open space concept for all the family gatherings.  A side area for your office space or family entertainment. Solar panels to save on the electric bill during the summer days and nights. The lot offers 19,950 sqft; enough space for RV parking, agriculture, horses, chickens and much more. Conveniently located near shopping center, Hesperia golf and country club, Hesperia Lake Park for your fishing, camping and out with the family trip. School nearby: Kingston Elementary, Ranchero Middle School and Sultan high school.
